I"0<h3 id="pre-requisites">Pre-Requisites</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Visual Studio Code - install it from the default Ubuntu Software Center</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="steps-to-configure-sfdx">Steps to configure SFDX</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Install OpenJDK 11 using the following terminal command
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> <span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>openjdk-11-jdk
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Set the environment variables using the following terminal commands
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> <span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">JAVA_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span>/usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk-amd64
 <span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$JAVA_HOME</span>
 <span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">PATH</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$PATH</span>:<span class="nv">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin
 <span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$PATH</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Check the java version in terminal
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> java <span class="nt">-version</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>
